title: Wisconsin Juggalo receives 3.5 years in prison | Daily Mail Online
text: show ad Insane Clown Posse fan receives 3.5 years in prison after he 'chopped his friend's pinky off with a machete to drink her blood in honor of a fallen Juggalo â€” before using a blowtorch to stop the bleeding' Jonathan Schrap, 24, faces receives 3.5 years in prison for chopping a friend's pinky off and drinking her blood in a 'ritualistic memorial' for a fallen Juggalo Schrap, of Wisconsin, appeared in a Brown County court room Friday morning for a sentencing hearing A judge appeared flabbergasted with the details of the case He was with a group of friends celebrating the death of a fellow Juggalo Shelby Neuens, 27, told police she let Schrap chop off her pinky Neuens only went to the hospital because her boyfriend's mom forced her She protested against the charges for her friend, insisting she volunteered Published: 15:21 GMT, 26 February 2017 | Updated: 15:46 GMT, 26 February 2017 122 shares
